<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>Vanilla launcher install</title>
<meta name="description" content="Install All the Mods 10 with the official (vanilla) Minecraft launcher and NeoForge, for players who do not use the CurseForge app.">
<style>
  :root {
    --bg:#14161a; --panel:#1e2128; --panel2:#262a33; --text:#e8eaed; --muted:#a7adba;
    --accent:#5db462; --accent2:#7fd884; --border:#333844; --code:#0f1115;
    --warn-bg:#3a2c14; --warn-border:#7a5a1e; --warn-text:#f4d58b;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
    :root {
      --bg:#f4f6f8; --panel:#fff; --panel2:#eef1f5; --text:#1b1e24; --muted:#566072;
      --accent:#2f8f43; --accent2:#257035; --border:#d7dde5; --code:#eef1f5;
      --warn-bg:#fff5db; --warn-border:#e2b657; --warn-text:#6b4e12;
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { margin:0; background:var(--bg); color:var(--text);
    font:16px/1.6 system-ui,-apple-system,Segoe UI,Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif; }
  .wrap { max-width:760px; margin:0 auto; padding:2rem 1.1rem 4rem; }
  a { color:var(--accent2); }
  h1 { font-size:1.8rem; margin:0.3rem 0 0.4rem; }
  h2 { font-size:1.3rem; margin:2.2rem 0 0.6rem; }
  h3 { font-size:1.05rem; margin:0 0 0.3rem; }
  p.lead { color:var(--muted); margin-top:0; }
  code { font-family:ui-monospace,Menlo,Consolas,monospace; background:var(--code);
    border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:5px; padding:0.05rem 0.35rem; }
  .card { background:var(--panel); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px;
    padding:1.1rem 1.3rem; margin:1.1rem 0; }
  .muted { color:var(--muted); }
  .em { color:var(--accent2); font-weight:600; }
  ol.steps { counter-reset: step; list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  ol.steps > li {
    position: relative; background: var(--panel); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 1.1rem 1.2rem 1.1rem 3.4rem; margin: 0.9rem 0;
  }
  ol.steps > li::before {
    counter-increment: step; content: counter(step);
    position: absolute; left: 1rem; top: 1.05rem;
    width: 1.7rem; height: 1.7rem; border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent); color: #06210b; font-weight: 700;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  ol.steps p { margin: 0.4rem 0; }
  footer { text-align:center; color:var(--muted); font-size:0.9rem; margin-top:3rem; }
  footer a { color:var(--muted); }
</style>
</head>
<body>
{{template "topnav" .}}
<div class="wrap">

  <h1>Install with the official (vanilla) launcher</h1>
  <p class="lead">This path is for players who do <span class="em">not</span> use the CurseForge app. It
  takes a little more setup, and you will need the client pack from the
  <a href="/portal/downloads">Downloads page in the member portal</a>. Keep the pack at version
  {{.PackVersion}} so it matches the server.</p>

  <h2>Set it up with the official Minecraft launcher</h2>

  <ol class="steps">

    <li>
      <h3>Install Java 21</h3>
      <p>The NeoForge installer needs it. Get Temurin 21 from <code>adoptium.net</code>.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Install NeoForge 21.1.234</h3>
      <p>Download the 21.1.234 installer from <code>neoforged.net</code>, run it, and choose
      <span class="em">Install client</span>. This adds a <span class="em">NeoForge 21.1.234</span>
      version to the Minecraft launcher.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Make a game folder</h3>
      <p>In the launcher, open <span class="em">Installations &rarr; New installation</span>, pick the
      version <span class="em">release 21.1.234</span> (NeoForge), and set the
      <span class="em">Game directory</span> to a new empty folder such as <code>C:\ATM10</code>.
      Under <span class="em">More options</span>, set the memory in the JVM arguments to at least
      <code>-Xmx8G</code> (10G recommended; needs a PC with about 16&nbsp;GB of RAM). Save.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Add the pack</h3>
      <p>Download the client pack from the Downloads page in the member portal and extract it into that
      folder, so you end up with <code>C:\ATM10\mods</code>, <code>C:\ATM10\config</code>, and
      <code>C:\ATM10\kubejs</code>.</p>
    </li>

    <li>
      <h3>Launch</h3>
      <p>Start the <span class="em">NeoForge 21.1.234</span> installation. The first launch takes a few
      minutes while it loads the mods.</p>
    </li>

  </ol>

  <h2>Connect</h2>
  <div class="card">
    <p>In <span class="em">Multiplayer &rarr; Add Server</span>, use this address:</p>
    <p><code>{{.ServerAddress}}</code></p>
    <p>If it will not connect, use the explicit address <code>{{.FallbackAddress}}</code> instead.</p>
    <p class="muted">The server is whitelist-only. Ask Dan to add you (or redeem an invite link)
    before you connect.</p>
  </div>

  <footer>
    <p><a href="/">Back to the main page</a> &middot; Prefer the CurseForge app? See the
    <a href="/curseforge">CurseForge install</a>.</p>
  </footer>

</div>
{{template "authscript" .}}
</body>
</html>
